<|channel>thought
<channel|># 懵然不知
(pos:成語/形容詞)
<explanation>
yue:完全唔知發生咩事，或者對某件事完全冇概念，處於一種發愣、唔清唔楚嘅狀態。
eng:to be completely unaware; to be in a state of confusion or cluelessness.
<eg>
yue:佢對發生緊嘅事完全係懵然不知，成個人呆咗喺度。 (keoi5 deoi3 faat3 sang1 gan2 ge3 si6 jyun4 cyun4 mung2 jin4 bat1 zi1, sing4 go3 jan4 daai4 zo2 hai2 dou6.)
eng:He is completely unaware of what is happening and is just standing there dazed. [end of text]


